@mariiaKraievska For improving the test:
"This test is not really testing whether only the schedule that fall on that particular date was rescheduled. You should check whether the following periods after the one that got rescheduled was not moved."

Feel free to raise an another PR for the same story. It is not crucial anymore.

@00RohitRoshan ... this Docker Compose file is **not** meant to pull the Docker Hub image of Apache Fineract. You need to build the Docker image locally and THEN you can start the Docker Compose stack.
Note: at the moment we don't provide regular updates to Docker Hub that's why this is the recommended way for now. But we are working on it (doing regular updates to Docker Hub).

Not an issue. Closing.
